## The Tragic Irony

The Third Era illustrates a deep irony in the lore:
- The system **worked** (Dragonfires = perfect protection)
- But it rested on **a single family** (the Septims)
- When that family dies, there is **no plan B**
- 433 years of security made people **complacent**
- The Mythic Dawn only needed to kill 4 people to destroy the protection of an entire world
